<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Secret Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            text-align: center;
        }

        div {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #ff4b5c;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #e03b4e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <h1>Welcome to the Secret Page</h1>
        <p>We are currently learning web technologies in our course, which is being taught by Sir Ali Hassan, a very knowledgeable and engaging teacher.</p>
        <form action="/logout" method="POST">
            <button type="submit">Logout</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
